data.description: NEW INTERIOR PAINT, NEW CARPET, AND NEW LINOLEUM IN BOTH BATHROOMS AND LAUNDRY ROOM!!!!!! Embrace your farm animals without worrying about a homeowners association (NO HOA) in this charming home nestled in a family neighborhood. A tranquil water creek graces the rear 0.8-acre, with a total lot size of 0.81 acres. Revel in the warmth of hardwood floors on the main level, new carpet in the bedrooms, and fresh linoleum in both bathrooms and the laundry room. Also, freshly painted interior. The slightly sloped backyard, adorned with mature trees, ensures a private atmosphere. Unwind and entertain in the backyard of this well-preserved residence, making it an ideal fit for a family just beginning their journey. MORE PICTURES COMING
